The 2021-22 UEFA Champions League group games are two match days away from Round of 16. So far, Liverpool of Group B, Ajax of Group C, Bayern Munich of Group E and Juventus plus Chelsea of Group H have all secured their places in the next stage. By contrast, other heavyweights like Paris Saint-Germain, Manchester United, Barcelona and Inter Milan are not lucky. One careless loss could easily cost their chance of carrying forward in the tournament. Host: Li Xiang Guest: Josh McNally Cover designer: Feng Yuan Chief editor: Chen Ran Supervisor: Zhang Shilei